# =============================================================================
# Design image binaries — keep on disk locally; do not commit to git
# =============================================================================
# Tracked on purpose:
#   prototype/project/favicon.svg
#   prototype/project/icons/icon-*.png

# Audit + iteration scratch captures (referenced by docs as local evidence only)
docs/design/**/*.jpeg
docs/design/**/*.jpg
docs/design/**/*.png
docs/design/**/*.webp
docs/design/**/*.gif

# Optional visual-regression baselines (see docs/design/screenshots/README.md)
docs/design/screenshots/*
!docs/design/screenshots/README.md
node_modules/
test-results/
playwright-report/
visual-regression-artifacts/
npm-debug.log*
snapshots/

# Windows reserved device names (cmd-style `2>nul` in bash creates a real file)
nul
NUL
con
CON
prn
PRN
aux
AUX
com[1-9]
COM[1-9]
lpt[1-9]
LPT[1-9]
